status				testing

title				Scanner framework
headline			Universal scanner interface
description
	SANE stands for "Scanner Access Now Easy" and is an application programming interface (API) that provides standardized access to any raster image scanner hardware (flatbed scanner, hand-held scanner, video- and still-cameras, frame-grabbers, etc.).
licenses			GPL+exception

home				www.sane-project.org
packages			sane-backends-1.0.20
locations
	ftp://ftp.sane-project.org/pub/sane/old-versions/sane-backends-1.0.20/
	ftp://ftp2.sane-project.org/pub/sane/old-versions/sane-backends-1.0.20/
	ftp://ftp.sane-project.org/pub/sane/sane-backends-1.0.20/
	ftp://ftp2.sane-project.org/pub/sane/sane-backends-1.0.20/
